Commands:
npm init ( for project create).
node index.js ( for run file ).
npm i dotenv ( create .env file )
npm express ( for add express Note : find command on offical site )
npm mongoes

For Create File and folder using command:
 
touch app.js index.js(for mac)
New-Item app.js -ItemType File(for win)
New-Item index.js -ItemType File(for win)
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Name folderName
'controllers','db','middlewares','models','routes','utils' | ForEach-Object { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Name $_ }
e)

npm i -D nodemon(For hot-relaod)

